    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Braced mouth bows of the Shona of Zimbabwe, made from a single stick of wood and with the string looped to the bow at its center.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
